sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant App
    participant Storage as SharedPreferences
    participant Hash as CryptoEngine
    
    User->>App: Opens App
    App->>Storage: Check for saved PIN hash
    Storage-->>App: Hash Exists
    App->>User: Show Lock Screen
    User->>App: Enters 1234
    App->>Hash: Hash("1234" + Salt)
    Hash-->>App: Computed Hash
    App->>App: Compare Computed == Stored
    App->>User: Unlock Dashboard
